VEDIC ASTROLOGY

This project implements principles and calculations from Vedic astrology (Jyotisha),
an ancient Indian system of astronomy and astrology. While the calculations are
mathematical and based on astronomical observations, astrology itself is a
pseudoscience. The results provided by this software should be considered
for entertainment and educational purposes only.

This software makes no claims of accuracy, reliability, or predictive power.
Users should not make important life decisions based solely on astrological
calculations provided by this software.

